type: software
title: "TRAP Attribution Extraction Scripts"
version: 1.0.0
date-released: 2025-11-23
abstract: |
  Python scripts and dataset for extracting field survey attribution data from
  TRAP (Tundzha Regional Archaeological Project) diaries and field documentation
  covering 2009-2011 Kazanluk field seasons. Provides complete attribution for
  268 survey days with 100% walker data coverage extracted from 15+ field diaries,
  39 survey unit PDFs, and Excel survey summaries.

