# Dataset information
dataset:
  title: "TRAP Archaeological Survey Attribution Data (2009-2011)"
  description: |
    Complete attribution dataset for 268 survey days from the Tundzha Regional
    Archaeological Project (TRAP) Kazanluk field seasons (2009-2011). Documents
    field walker participation, team compositions, leadership, and survey unit
    assignments extracted from primary source diaries and field documentation.
  format: CSV
  size: 268 records
  coverage: "100% walker data coverage"

